name: POLO RALPH LAUREN
description:
*NOTE: This is a special occasion where I mint more than 1 piece, I am an artist who only does 1/1.

This is my work for the #hen600k, a piece I've been wanting to upload for a while but couldn't find the occasion. It is a work that I like very much because it represents something very important to me, my favorite clothing brand for some years, POLO RALPH LAUREN. I collect pieces of the brand as if they were yu-gi-oh cards, it's always a constant search, I'm fascinated by all the history behind it and it always inspires me to create works that I keep private, maybe in the future I'll start to publish them here.
